installSteps:
Add to your OpenClaw skill config:
```json
{
  "skills": ["gog"]
}
```

Add to your agent config:
```json
{
  "skills": ["apple-reminders"]
}
```

Add to your agent config:
```json
{
  "skills": ["apple-notes"]
}
```

Weather is a built-in skill with no dependencies. Add to your agent config:
```json
{
  "skills": ["weather"]
}
```

Add to your agent config with vault path:
```json
{
  "skills": ["obsidian"],
  "config": {
    "obsidian": {
      "vaultPath": "~/Documents/ObsidianVault"
    }
  }
}
```

Humanizer is a built-in skill. Add to your agent config:
```json
{
  "skills": ["humanizer"]
}
```

X Post Drafter is a built-in skill. Add to your agent config:
```json
{
  "skills": ["x-post"]
}
```

Optionally configure an Obsidian vault for draft storage:
```json
{
  "config": {
    "obsidian": {
      "vaultPath": "~/Documents/ObsidianVault"
    }
  }
}
```

